    "body": "``` javascript\nipc.on('settings-appearance-widget-all-workspaces', (event, show) => {\n    process.storage.set(show, C.ALLWORKSPACES, C.APPEARANCE);\n    process.storage.save(false);\n    console.log('before');\n    console.log(process.windows.widget.isVisibleOnAllWorkspaces());\n    process.windows.widget.setVisibleOnAllWorkspaces(show);\n    console.log('after');\n    console.log(process.windows.widget.isVisibleOnAllWorkspaces());\n});\n```\n\nIt will return correct values when switching between visible and non visible on all Workspaces, but it always show my widget on all Workspaces:\n\n``` javascript\nbefore\nfalse\nafter\ntrue\n\nbefore\ntrue\nafter\nfalse\n```\n"
